description: Demolition of hospital buildings (excluding locally listed building),  houses on Tollington Way and  Gloucester House. Construction of 205 flats and 35 houses and layout of new public open space. Applicants Plan Nos:  10925C/05A,10A,11-34

CONDITION: The development hereby permitted shall be begun not later than the expiration of five years from the date of this permission. 

 REASON: To comply with the provisions of Section 91(1) of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990.
